{"title_page": "Henry Kiprono Kirwa", "text_new": "{{short description|Kenyan Paralympic athlete}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name = Henry Kirwa\n| image = Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics \u2013 Men's 1500 metres T13.jpg\n| caption = Kirwa (number 4) in the men's 1500 metres T13 final at the 2008 Summer Paralympics\n| headercolor = lightsteelblue\n| full_name = Henry Kiprono Kirwa\n| birth_date = {{Birth-date and age|4 May 1973}}\n| birth_place =\n| disability_class = [[T12 (classification)|T12]], [[T13 (classification)|T13]]\n| medaltemplates = \n{{MedalSport | Men's [[para athletics]]}}\n{{MedalCountry|{{KEN}}}}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[Paralympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 1500 metres - T13|1500m - T13]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 5000 metres - T13|5000m - T13]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 10000 metres - T12|10000m - T12]]}}\n}}\n\n'''Henry Kiprono Kirwa''' (born 4 May 1973) is a [[Paralympian]] [[Track and field|athlete]] from [[Kenya]] competing mainly in category T13 middle distance events.\n\nHe competed in the [[2008 Summer Paralympics]] in [[Beijing]], [[People's Republic of China|China]].  There he won a gold medal in the men's 1500 metres - T13 event, a gold medal in the men's 5000 metres - T13 event and a gold medal in the men's 10000 metres - T12 event\n\n==External links==\n* {{IPC athlete|henry-kirwa|Henry Kirwa|old_id=966378}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kirwa, Henry Kiprono}}\n[[Category:Paralympic athletes of Kenya]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2008 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Kenya]]\n[[Category:Kenyan male middle-distance runners]]\n[[Category:Kenyan male long-distance runners]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2008 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2012 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:1973 births]]\n\n\n{{Kenya-athletics-bio-stub}}\n{{Paralympic-medalist-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Kenyan Paralympic athlete}}\n[[File:Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics \u2013 Men's 1500 metres T13.jpg|thumb|Henry Kiprono Kirwa (number 4) in the men's 1500 metres T13 final at the 2008 Summer Paralympics]]\n{{MedalTableTop}}\n{{MedalSport | [[Track and field]] (T13)}}\n{{MedalCountry|{{KEN}}}}\n{{MedalCompetition|[[Paralympic Games]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 1500 metres - T13|1500m - T13]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 5000 metres - T13|5000m - T13]]}}\n{{MedalGold| [[2008 Summer Paralympics|2008 Beijing]] | [[Athletics at the 2008 Summer Paralympics - Men's 10000 metres - T12|10000m - T12]]}}\n{{MedalBottom}}\n\n'''Henry Kiprono Kirwa''' (born 4 May 1973) is a [[Paralympian]] [[Track and field|athlete]] from [[Kenya]] competing mainly in category T13 middle distance events.\n\nHe competed in the [[2008 Summer Paralympics]] in [[Beijing]], [[People's Republic of China|China]].  There he won a gold medal in the men's 1500 metres - T13 event, a gold medal in the men's 5000 metres - T13 event and a gold medal in the men's 10000 metres - T12 event\n\n==External links==\n* {{IPC athlete|966378|Henry Kirwa}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kirwa, Henry Kiprono}}\n[[Category:Paralympic athletes of Kenya]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2008 Summer Paralympics]]\n[[Category:Paralympic gold medalists for Kenya]]\n[[Category:Kenyan male middle-distance runners]]\n[[Category:Kenyan male long-distance runners]]\n[[Category:Li